author: hwright
msg: More propcaching extraction.  This makes it such that none of the propcaching
fields of svn_wc_entry_t are propulated in wc-ng.
(svn_wc__install_props): Don't modify the propcaching fields in the given
(svn_wc__working_props_committed): Don't change the has_prop_mods flag of
(svn_wc_prop_list): Load the base props and the current props and merge
them into the current prop list.
(svn_wc_prop_get): Remove any use of cached props.
Add these headers, so we can still read old log files.
(log_do_committed): Don't set has_prop_mods member of the entry.
(svn_wc__loggy_entry_modify): Don't handle any of the propcaching members.
